snippet.title: Bethel Christian Centre Ball Green
snippet.description:
This channel has been opened to discuss the incredible truths that are found within the pages of The Holy Bible from Genesis to Revelation. I am Tim the Pastor of Bethel Christian Centre, Ball Green along with my wonderful wife Mandy we hope to share some amazing stuff with you.
We will be having Interviews,Testimonies, Compact Messages, Studies, 
Prophetic Challenges, Trumpet cries, Apologetics, Controversies, Discussion Forums. We believe God will challenge us together as we get serious about what we believe and why we believe it...
